com.acrolinx.javasdk.gui.dialogs.options

Interface OptionContentPresenter.CheckTabView

  • All Known Subinterfaces:
    AcrolinxOptionsPreferenceView, OptionContentPresenter.OptionContentView, OptionPresenter.OptionView
    All Known Implementing Classes:
    AcrolinxOptionsPreferencePage, CheckOptionsComposite, CheckOptionsPanel, OptionDialog, OptionDialog
    Enclosing class:
    OptionContentPresenter

    public static interface OptionContentPresenter.CheckTabView
    The OptionContentPresenter.CheckTabView is the Part of the OptionContentPresenter.OptionContentView displaying all check settings. It is normally displayed at Check-Tab.
